  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK374">
<l>iruvē ṟulakat tiyaṟkai tiruvēṟu</l>
<l>teḷḷiya rātalum vēṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are (through fate) two different natures in the world, hence the difference (observable in men) in (their acquisition of) wealth, and in their attainment of knowledge.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
